order_number.orig_str: शासन निर्णय क्रमांकः स्थापना-२०२३/ प्र.क्र.१०६/ आरोग्य-४

para_trans: Mauje Jarandi, Ta. Regarding sanction of new Primary Health Centre at Tasgaon, District Sangli as a special case.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2023 / Q.106 / Health-4

Read: - Letter from Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries) Mumbai No: ASHA / Room-7A / TE-8 / Jrandi / Pre-Centre / Establishment / Sangli / 3512-14/2022, dated 16.09.2022.

Preface: - Mouje Jharandi, Ta. The government was considering sanctioning a primary health centre at Tasgaon as it was necessary to sanction a new primary health centre in order to provide health facilities to the citizens of the district and Sangli.
Government Decision: - Mouje Jarandi, Ta. Approval is being given to sanction a new Primary Health Centre at Tasgaon, District Sangli as a "special case."
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
